            {
                "s2_paper_id": "cc044999dc9de12f2b93fe6342cafa3289e10ea2",
                "title": "Level and influencing factors of transition shock among new nurses in China: A multicenter cross\u2010sectional study",
                "year": 2023,
                "venue": "Health Science Reports",
                "citation_count": 17,
                "reference_count": 33,
                "abstract": "New nurses are an important part of nursing teams. The failure of new nurses to successfully transition seriously affects personal career development and nursing work quality, and important influencing factors deserve the attention of nursing managers. At present, multicenter, large\u2010sample investigations of transition shock among new nurses are lacking in China. This study aims to investigate the current level and influencing factors of transition shock among new nurses in China.",
